data.description: Nestled within a serene and quiet subdivision, this meticulously maintained home boasts nearly 2700 square feet of living space, featuring four spacious bedrooms and three full bathrooms. The property offers a private backyard adorned by majestic mature trees, creating a tranquil oasis. Outdoor enthusiasts will delight in the rear deck and charming paver patio complete with a pergola. Inside, the unique open floor plan floods the living spaces with abundant natural light, enhancing the sense of openness and comfort. With its pristine condition and a large, wooded lot, this home combines both functionality & aesthetics.  Covered front porch and a finished 2 car attached garage.  Some of the updates include Quartz counter tops, Brazilian Cherry floors throughout and interior paint.
